{"tid":438884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"布吉機場無王管 員工狂摷行李要乜偷乜","createTime":"2017-10-17T10:42:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T09:17:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"ddd80acc3553ee4378fea0b535717d22bda16029","tid":438884,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T10:42:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20171017/20185765\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20171017%2F20185765&d=0Rz6KV7ikgSXxF%2BtUSPczghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=1661e4a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20171017%2F20185765&h=2d86cae6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20171017/20185765</a><br />\n<br />\n布吉機場無王管<br />\n員工狂摷行李要乜偷乜<br />\n<br />\n13,975<br />\n<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n泰國社交網日前廣傳一段影片，拍到布吉機場工作人員肆意打開並翻找多位乘客的行李再偷竊，賊人已被拘捕，並交回一個偷走的藍牙喇叭。<br />\n<br />\n事發在上周二下午3時多，一名外判行李處理員整理捷星航空（JetStar）一班準備飛往新加坡客機上的行李時，趁機偷取乘客財物。他打開數個未有上鎖的行李箱，伸手左找右找搜尋貴重品，連小袋子也不放過逐一打開細看。<br />\n<br />\n由影片可見賊人明知有人看到仍繼續偷竊，而且與拍片人互有傾談。當地傳媒報道賊人是27歲、名為阿敦羅的北大年府人，暫時未知他會有甚麼處分。<br />\n<br />\n泰國《世界日報》/英國《每日鏡報》  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n【動畫】亞航客機高空急墜　空姐喊住尖叫嚇壞乘客<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n傳哈里女友辭演《Suits》　聖誕前或宣佈訂婚"},{"pid":"893156dc07da35b6ebeac0625ee0abb8217feb79","tid":438884,"uid":25148,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T11:45:09.000Z","msg":"未有上鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb219b5f04ae22a41f95f9020e7982a773584fd","tid":438884,"uid":26003,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T12:21:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未有上鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一支原子筆搞掂你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fbb2ac6af37867f567f4173992967ee62384a6d","tid":4388